{
    "nodes": [
        {
            "parameters": {
                "jsCode": "// Filter leads: uncontacted + has phone number\n// Limits to 40 leads per batch\nconst items = $input.all();\nconst uncontacted = [];\nconst DAILY_LIMIT = 40;\n\nfor (const item of items) {\n  const status = (item.json.status || '').toString().toLowerCase().trim();\n  const phone = (item.json.phone || '').toString().trim();\n  \n  // Skip already contacted or no phone\n  if (['contacted', 'replied', 'converted', 'not_interested'].includes(status)) continue;\n  if (!phone || phone.length < 8) continue;\n  \n  // Clean phone for WhatsApp (must be 91XXXXXXXXXX)\n  let cleanPhone = phone.replace(/[^0-9+]/g, '');\n  if (cleanPhone.startsWith('+91')) cleanPhone = cleanPhone.substring(1);\n  else if (cleanPhone.startsWith('0')) cleanPhone = '91' + cleanPhone.substring(1);\n  else if (!cleanPhone.startsWith('91') && cleanPhone.length === 10) cleanPhone = '91' + cleanPhone;\n  \n  // Need at least 12 digits (91 + 10)\n  if (cleanPhone.length < 12) continue;\n\n  uncontacted.push({\n    json: {\n      business_name: item.json.business_name || 'Business',\n      category: item.json.category || '',\n      city: item.json.city || '',\n      phone: phone,\n      email: item.json.email || '',\n      website: item.json.website || '',\n      google_maps_url: item.json.google_maps_url || '',\n      rating: item.json.rating || '',\n      clean_phone: cleanPhone,\n      row_number: items.indexOf(item) + 2\n    }\n  });\n  \n  if (uncontacted.length >= DAILY_LIMIT) break;\n}\n\nreturn uncontacted;"
            },
            "id": "filter-code-1",
            "name": "Filter Uncontacted",
            "position": [
                480,
                400
            ],
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
            "typeVersion": 2
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": "https://integrate.api.nvidia.com/v1/chat/completions",
                "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
                "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
                "sendBody": true,
                "specifyBody": "json",
                "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"mistralai/mixtral-8x22b-instruct-v0.1\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 500,\n  \"temperature\": 0.8,\n  \"top_p\": 0.95,\n  \"stream\": false,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"You are Vikash — a young, skilled AI automation expert from Jaipur who builds smart business systems. You write WhatsApp outreach messages that feel personal, valuable, and impossible to ignore.\\n\\nMESSAGE STRUCTURE (4-5 lines, 70-100 words):\\n\\nLine 1: Warm greeting + their exact business name + genuine compliment (mention their rating, area, or something specific about their category)\\n\\nLine 2-3: Show you researched them — reference their specific business type and a real challenge they likely face (e.g. restaurants struggle with late-night orders, cafes need consistent Instagram content, hotels miss booking inquiries after hours)\\n\\nLine 4-5: Present ONE specific AI automation with a concrete result. Be specific with numbers.\\n\\nLine 6: Soft CTA question — curious, not pushy\\n\\nLine 7: Sign off as - Vikash\\n\\nWHAT TO OFFER — DEPENDS ON WEBSITE STATUS:\\n\\nIF THEY HAVE A WEBSITE (website field is not empty/None):\\nDO NOT offer website or digital presence. They already have one. Instead offer ONE of these AI automations:\\n\\n1. WhatsApp AI Chatbot — handles customer queries, menu browsing, table bookings, and orders 24/7 automatically. They never miss a customer even at 2 AM. Mention: reduces response time from hours to seconds.\\n2. AI Review Responder — automatically crafts personalized replies to every Google and Zomato review within minutes. Boosts their search ranking and shows customers they care.\\n3. AI Social Media Manager — generates and posts Instagram/Facebook content (photos, captions, stories, reels ideas) on autopilot. Consistent posting without hiring a social media person.\\n4. WhatsApp Ordering System — customers browse menu, customize orders, and pay directly via WhatsApp chat. No app download needed. Increases orders by 30-40%.\\n5. AI Customer Follow-up System — automatically sends personalized 'we miss you' messages to customers who haven't visited in 2+ weeks. Brings back 15-20% of inactive customers.\\n6. AI-powered Google Business Profile — auto-posts updates, responds to Q&A, and keeps the profile active. Higher Maps ranking = more walk-in customers.\\n\\nPick the MOST relevant one based on business type:\\n- Restaurants/Cafes → WhatsApp ordering + AI chatbot for after-hours\\n- Hotels/Resorts → AI booking assistant + review responder\\n- Bakeries/Sweet shops → WhatsApp catalog + social media automation\\n- Salons/Spas → AI appointment booking + customer follow-up\\n- Retail/Shops → WhatsApp product catalog + personalized offers\\n- Gyms/Fitness → AI membership bot + follow-up system\\n\\nIF THEY HAVE NO WEBSITE (website is None/empty):\\nOffer a combo: professional website + ONE AI automation. Mention that 73% of customers search online before visiting, and they are losing customers every day without a web presence.\\n\\nTONE RULES:\\n- Sound like a confident, knowledgeable young entrepreneur who genuinely wants to help — NOT a salesperson or spammer\\n- Conversational Indian English — okay to use light Hindi words naturally like 'aapki', 'bhai', 'ji' if it fits\\n- Include ONE specific number or stat to build credibility (e.g. '24/7 availability', '3x faster response', '30% more orders', 'saves 2 hours daily')\\n- Make them feel this is a personal message, not a mass blast\\n- Use 2-3 emojis naturally — dont overdo\\n- NEVER use [brackets], {curly braces}, or {{placeholders}} in your output\\n- NEVER say 'Dear Sir/Madam', 'I hope this message finds you well', 'We are a leading company'\\n- NEVER sound like a corporate pitch or template\\n- The message should feel like a friend who happens to be tech-savvy is genuinely offering help\\n- End with: - Vikash\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"Write a WhatsApp outreach message for this business:\\n\\nBusiness Name: {{ $json.business_name }}\\nCategory/Type: {{ $json.category }}\\nCity: {{ $json.city }}\\nGoogle Rating: {{ $json.rating }}/5 stars\\nWebsite: {{ $json.website || 'NO WEBSITE — they need one!' }}\\nHas Website: {{ $json.website ? 'YES — do NOT offer website, offer AI automations only' : 'NO — offer website + AI automation combo' }}\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
                "options": {
                    "response": {
                        "response": {
                            "responseFormat": "json"
                        }
                    }
                }
            },
